\newlabel{fig:rq1_qualitative_reconstructions}{{6}{9}{Ground-truth MIPs, retained-payload reconstructions, and pixelwise absolute differences for five pretrained blocks at 10\%, 50\%, and 100\% Gaussian retention. Each row represents one block. GT and reconstruction panels share the response scale, while all difference panels share the separate error scale}{figure.caption.10}{}}
